---
// SectionLaCima.astro — Sección final / "La Cima"
---

<section id="summit" class="summit-section">
  <div class="content-container summit-grid">
    <div class="summit-text">
      <div class="top-badge">¡Has llegado a la cima!</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">La Cima</h2>
      <p class="summit-quote">
        «Las mejores vistas llegan tras la escalada más dura.»
      </p>
      <button class="btn-secondary">Únete al Club</button>
    </div>
    <div class="summit-contact">
      <h3>Preguntas y consultas</h3>
      <button class="btn-outline">MÁNDANOS UN MENSAJE</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer class="main-footer">
    &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Club Alpino Ama Dablam. Elevando el potencial
    humano.
  </footer>
</section>

<style>
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  .summit-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .summit-grid {
      gap: 3rem;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .summit-text {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .summit-text {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  .top-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #fff;
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 900;
    padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .summit-quote {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #d1d5db;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .summit-quote {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    background-color: #fff;
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      background-color 0.3s,
      color 0.3s;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background-color: var(--clr-main);
  }

  .summit-contact {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--clr-main);
  }

  .summit-contact h3 {
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #fff;
    background: transparent;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    background-color: #fff;
    color: #000;
  }

  .main-footer {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--clr-main);
    color: var(--clr-main);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
</style>
